                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
                                If you didn't create an account with Tuned Essays, you can safely ignore this email.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    
